## The Challenge

| Problem | Solution |
|---|---|
| 135:1 class imbalance | SMOTE oversampling at 10% ratio |
| Raw flux values vary per star | Per-star normalisation (axis=1) |
| Overfitting on rare class | Dropout (0.5) + early stopping |
| Unstable gradients | Gradient clipping + LR scheduler |
| No middle ground threshold | Threshold tuning across 0.3–0.7 |

---

## Model Architecture — TunedCNN

```
Input (1 × 3197)
    ↓  Conv1D(1→32, k=5) + BatchNorm + ReLU + MaxPool
    ↓  Conv1D(32→64, k=5) + BatchNorm + ReLU + MaxPool
    ↓  Conv1D(64→128, k=3) + BatchNorm + ReLU + MaxPool
    ↓  AdaptiveAvgPool → (128,)
    ↓  Linear(128→64) + ReLU + Dropout(0.5)
    ↓  Linear(64→1) + Sigmoid
Output: probability of exoplanet transit
```

